      "path": "audio/narrations/newton-method/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-1.mp3",
      "duration": 0.97,
      "size": 15552,
      "text": "欢迎来到牛顿法实验。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "newton-method",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-2",
      "filename": "intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/newton-method/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.65,
      "size": 42336,
      "text": "如何求解方程f(x)=0？对于简单的方程，我们可以用代数方法。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "newton-method",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-3",
      "filename": "intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/newton-method/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.84,
      "size": 45504,
      "text": "但对于复杂的方程，比如x的五次方加x等于1，代数方法就无能为力了。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "newton-method",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-4",
      "filename": "intro-intro-4.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/newton-method/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-4.mp3",
      "duration": 1.45,
      "size": 23184,
      "text": "牛顿法提供了一种强大的数值求解方法。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "newton-method",
      "section_id": "concept",
      "line_id": "concept-1",
      "filename": "concept-concept-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/newton-method/xiaoxiao/concept-concept-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.58,
      "size": 25344,
      "text": "牛顿法的核心思想是用切线来逼近曲线。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "newton-method",
      "section_id": "concept",
      "line_id": "concept-2",
      "filename": "concept-concept-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/newton-method/xiaoxiao/concept-concept-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.55,
      "size": 24768,
      "text": "从一个初始猜测开始，画出该点的切线。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "newton-method",
      "section_id": "concept",
      "line_id": "concept-3",
      "filename": "concept-concept-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/newton-method/xiaoxiao/concept-concept-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.62,
      "size": 25920,
      "text": "切线与x轴的交点就是下一个更好的近似。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "newton-method",
      "section_id": "concept",
      "line_id": "concept-4",
      "filename": "concept-concept-4.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/newton-method/xiaoxiao/concept-concept-4.mp3",
      "duration": 1.66,
      "size": 26496,
      "text": "重复这个过程，通常能快速收敛到真正的根。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "newton-method",
      "section_id": "visualization",
      "line_id": "vis-1",
      "filename": "visualization-vis-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/newton-method/xiaoxiao/visualization-vis-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.4,
      "size": 22464,
      "text": "让我们在图上观察牛顿法的迭代过程。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "newton-method",
      "section_id": "visualization",
      "line_id": "vis-2",
      "filename": "visualization-vis-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/newton-method/xiaoxiao/visualization-vis-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.65,
      "size": 26352,
      "text": "红点是当前的近似值，蓝线是该点的切线。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "newton-method",
      "section_id": "visualization",
      "line_id": "vis-3",
      "filename": "visualization-vis-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/newton-method/xiaoxiao/visualization-vis-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.5,
      "size": 24048,
      "text": "切线与x轴的交点成为新的近似值。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "newton-method",
      "section_id": "visualization",
      "line_id": "vis-4",
      "filename": "visualization-vis-4.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/newton-method/xiaoxiao/visualization-vis-4.mp3",
      "duration": 1.84,
      "size": 29520,
      "text": "注意每次迭代后，近似值如何快速接近真正的根。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "newton-method",
      "section_id": "convergence",
      "line_id": "conv-1",
      "filename": "convergence-conv-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/newton-method/xiaoxiao/convergence-conv-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.52,
      "size": 24336,
      "text": "牛顿法的收敛速度是二次的，非常快。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "newton-method",
      "section_id": "convergence",
      "line_id": "conv-2",
      "filename": "convergence-conv-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/newton-method/xiaoxiao/convergence-conv-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.63,
      "size": 26064,
      "text": "这意味着每次迭代，正确的位数大约翻倍。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "newton-method",
      "section_id": "convergence",
      "line_id": "conv-3",
      "filename": "convergence-conv-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/newton-method/xiaoxiao/convergence-conv-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.12,
      "size": 33984,
      "text": "但牛顿法也可能失败：如果初始点选得不好，可能不收敛。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "newton-method",
      "section_id": "convergence",
      "line_id": "conv-4",
      "filename": "convergence-conv-4.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/newton-method/xiaoxiao/convergence-conv-4.mp3",
      "duration": 1.6,
      "size": 25632,
      "text": "在导数为零的点附近，牛顿法也会出问题。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "newton-method",
      "section_id": "application",
      "line_id": "app-1",
      "filename": "application-app-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/newton-method/xiaoxiao/application-app-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.61,
      "size": 25776,
      "text": "牛顿法是数值计算中最重要的算法之一。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "newton-method",
      "section_id": "application",
      "line_id": "app-2",
      "filename": "application-app-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/newton-method/xiaoxiao/application-app-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.86,
      "size": 29808,
      "text": "计算器和计算机用它来计算平方根和其他函数。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "newton-method",
      "section_id": "application",
      "line_id": "app-3",
      "filename": "application-app-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/newton-method/xiaoxiao/application-app-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.49,
      "size": 23904,
      "text": "优化问题中，它用于寻找函数的极值点。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "newton-method",
      "section_id": "application",
      "line_id": "app-4",
      "filename": "application-app-4.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/newton-method/xiaoxiao/application-app-4.mp3",
      "duration": 1.74,
      "size": 27792,
      "text": "机器学习中的许多优化算法都是牛顿法的变体。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "newton-method",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-1",
      "filename": "summary-sum-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/newton-method/xiaoxiao/summary-sum-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.34,
      "size": 21456,
      "text": "今天我们探索了牛顿法的原理和应用。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "newton-method",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-2",
      "filename": "summary-sum-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/newton-method/xiaoxiao/summary-sum-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.7,
      "size": 27216,
      "text": "它用切线逼近的思想，实现了快速的迭代求根。"
    },
    {
